# DevCapsule project declarations and platform locks are repository inputs.
# Keep them visible even when a developer has a broad .devcapsule ignore in a
# global Git excludes file. Developer-owned checkout and resolved files live
# beneath the XDG configuration root, not in this directory.
!/.devcapsule/
!/.devcapsule/devcapsule.toml
!/.devcapsule/devcapsule.*.lock
